            .icons: span
            .title subheading.pug
            pre.language-jade
              code.
                h1 ...
                h3(class="subheading muted") ...

          // Paragraph
          h3#h-paragraph.demo-head Paragraph
          p
            |除了特殊規範外, 所有的段落文字使用&nbsp;
            code 13px
